<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="page-main">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-header centered">
      <h1>How Ringatrade Works</h1>
      <p>Getting matched with a local tradesperson is quick and simple.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw-steps">
      <div class="hiw-step">
        <div class="hiw-step-num">1</div>
        <div class="hiw-step-content">
          <h2>Tell us the job</h2>
          <p>Fill in our short job request form. Tell us what trade you need, describe the work, enter your postcode, and let us know how urgent it is. It takes about two minutes.</p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Select the type of trade needed</li>
            <li>Describe the job in plain English</li>
            <li>Enter your postcode so we can find local trades</li>
            <li>Tell us how urgently you need the work done</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hiw-step">
        <div class="hiw-step-num">2</div>
        <div class="hiw-step-content">
          <h2>We review and match it</h2>
          <p>Once we receive your request, we review the details and look for suitable local tradespeople in your area who cover your type of work.</p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>We check your job details and location</li>
            <li>We identify relevant local tradespeople</li>
            <li>We pass your contact details and job description to suitable tradespeople</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hiw-step">
        <div class="hiw-step-num">3</div>
        <div class="hiw-step-content">
          <h2>A tradesperson contacts you</h2>
          <p>A suitable tradesperson will get in touch with you via your preferred contact method — phone, email, or WhatsApp. You can then discuss the job, agree on pricing, and arrange a visit.</p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Tradesperson contacts you via your preferred method</li>
            <li>Discuss the job and get a quote</li>
            <li>Arrange a time that suits you</li>
            <li>No obligation — you decide whether to proceed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw-cta">
      <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
      <p>Post your job for free — no signup required.</p>
      <a href="/post-a-job" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Post a Job</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
